data.title: Solarization of Feeder
data.description: Given the high power purchase rate for the respective DISCOM, extent feeder segregation, and penetration of electric pumps, solarization of feeder would be the way to promote solar-powered irrigation in Anantapur. It would ensure rapid and efficient solarization of irrigation power at large scale.
